Description: GTK reminder app with flexible scheduling
 Tray reminder application supporting one-time, interval and
 calendar-based reminders with desktop notifications.
 .
 Lives in the system tray via AppIndicator (Ayatana with a fallback to
 the legacy AppIndicator3), shows notifications through libnotify, and
 stores reminders locally in SQLite.
